<h3 class="teaser_headline"><a href="/entity/neglected_diseases/vector_ecology/mosquito-borne-diseases/en/index.html">Deadliest animal in the world</a></h3> 
<p>
	<span> Mosquitoes are one of the deadliest animals in the world. Their ability to carry and spread disease to humans causes millions of deaths every year. Zika, yellow fever, dengue, chikungunya, malaria, and West Nile virus are just some of these diseases.</span>
</p>	
