	<h2 class="module_title">
Highlights	</h2>
      <ul class="list">
	</ul>

      <ul class="list">
				<li>
	<a  href="/entity/tb/publications/lamp-diagnosis-molecular/en/index.html">Diagnosis of pulmonary TB</a><br/><span class="link_info">August 2016 -- WHO recommends the use of loop-mediated isothermal amplification (TB-LAMP) for the diagnosis of pulmonary tuberculosis.  It can also be considered as a follow-on test to microscopy in adults with signs and symptoms of pulmonary TB.</span>
				</li>
	</ul>

